---
import Page from '../layouts/Page.astro'
import { site } from '../lib/site'
---

<Page title="CV — Serina McFall" description="Curriculum vitae for Serina McFall — junior developer, accessibility-first, Auckland-based.">
  <article class="cv">
    <p class="download-bar">
      <a href="/serina-mcfall-cv.pdf" download="serina-mcfall-cv.pdf" class="download-btn">
        Download CV (PDF)
      </a>
    </p>
    <header class="cv-head">
  <div>
    <h1>Serina McFall</h1>
    <p class="role">Junior developer · accessibility-first · neurospicy</p>
  </div>
  <ul class="contact">
    <li><a href={site.url}>vixenz.dev</a></li>
    <li><a href={`mailto:${site.email}`}>{site.email}</a></li>
    <li><a href={site.github}>GitHub</a></li>
    <li><a href={site.linkedin}>LinkedIn</a></li>
    <li>{site.location}</li>
  </ul>
</header>

 <section>
  <h2>Skills</h2>
  <dl class="skills">
    <div>
      <dt>Frontend</dt>
      <dd>React, JavaScript, TypeScript, Astro, CSS, semantic HTML, WCAG 2.2, W3C APG patterns</dd>
    </div>
    <div>
      <dt>Backend</dt>
      <dd>Express, REST APIs, Integration testing</dd>
    </div>
    <div>
      <dt>Databases</dt>
      <dd>SQL (SQLite, Postgres via Supabase), schema design, Knex migrations + seeds, indexing strategies</dd>
    </div>
    <div>
      <dt>Tooling</dt>
      <dd>Vite, Vitest, Playwright, axe-core, Git, Cloudflare Pages, Vercel, Anthropic / OpenAI APIs (used in my Dev Academy ai-chatbot project)</dd>
    </div>
    <div>
      <dt>Practice</dt>
      <dd>TDD where it helps, scaffold-first learning, design-doc-driven work, accessibility audits. Currently learning: AI agent + worker patterns for the Learning Companion Project.</dd>
    </div>
  </dl>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>Projects</h2>
  <ul class="projects">
    <li>
      <strong>Atlas — visual concept library.</strong>
      A bootcamp shell (<code>art-gallery</code>) reworked into a living, accessibility-first concept library. <a href={`${site.url}/work/atlas`}>vixenz.dev/work/atlas</a>
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>The MTG Project.</strong>
      Eight design docs for a Commander deck-builder. Tech stack, schema, and architecture fully designed. <a href={`${site.url}/work/mtg-project`}>vixenz.dev/work/mtg-project</a>
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Avalúne Compendium.</strong>
      Express + Knex + SQLite practice backend with real worldbuilding canon. <a href={`${site.url}/work/avalune-compendium`}>vixenz.dev/work/avalune-compendium</a>
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Realmstack.</strong>
      A co-built project with my husband. Cloudflare Workers (D1, KV, R2), TypeScript. Doc-led planning phase — declaration, explainers, and research docs taking shape; implementation begins from there. <a href="https://realmstack.world">realmstack.world</a>
    </li>
  </ul>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>Education</h2>
  <p><strong>Dev Academy Aotearoa — AI Launchpad</strong> — 16-week agentic coding programme: multi-agent workflows on production codebases, industry placement with a NZ tech company. 27 July – 13 November 2026.</p>
  <p><strong>Dev Academy Aotearoa</strong> — full-stack web development bootcamp. Completed 2026.</p>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>Background</h2>
  <p>This is a career change. I spent the last decade in customer service and hospitality. The skills I'm bringing across: working with people under pressure, real-time problem-solving, communication, and reading what someone needs before they say it — the same instinct that drives accessibility-first design.</p>
</section>

  </article>
</Page>

<style>

  .cv {
    max-width: 48rem;

  }

  .download-bar {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: flex-end;
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
  }

  .download-btn {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-ui);
    color: var(--moonlight);
    background: var(--surface-card);
    backdrop-filter: blur(var(--surface-card-blur));
    padding: 0.5rem 0.9rem;
    border-radius: 6px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: box-shadow 200ms ease, transform 200ms ease;
  }

  .download-btn:hover,
  .download-btn:focus-visible {
    box-shadow: 0 0 16px rgba(232, 180, 196, 0.35);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  .download-btn:focus-visible {
    outline: 2px solid var(--magnolia);
    outline-offset: 4px;
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .download-btn {
      transition: none;
    }
    .download-btn:hover,
    .download-btn:focus-visible {
      transform: none;
    }
  }

  .cv-head {
    display:flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--tile-border);
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;

  }

  .cv-head h1 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;

  }

  .role {
    color: var(--mist);
    font-size: var(--text-ui);


  }

  .contact {
    list-style: none;
    text-align: right;
    font-size: var(--text-ui);
    color: var(--mist);

  }

  .contact a {
  display: inline-block;
  padding: 4px 0;
}

  .cv .projects, .cv .other {
    list-style: none;
    display:grid;
    gap:0.625rem

  }

  .cv .projects li, .cv .other li {
    color: var(--mist);
    max-width: none;

  }

  .cv .projects strong {
    color: var(--moonlight);
    font-weight: 600;
    
  }

  .cv section {
    margin: 1.25rem 0;

  }

  .cv h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-meta);
    color: var(--lotus);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 0.625rem;
  }

  .cv dl {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .cv dl div {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 8rem 1fr;
    gap: 1rem;
    align-items: baseline;
  }

  .cv dt {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-meta);
    color: var(--lotus);
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .cv dd {
    color: var(--moonlight);
  }

  @media (max-width: 36rem) {
    .cv-head { flex-direction: column; }
    .contact { text-align: left; }
    .cv dl div { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }

  @media print {
    .download-bar {
      display: none !important;
    }
    :global(.atmosphere) {
      display: none !important;
    }
    :root {
      --midnight: #ffffff;
      --moonlight: #1a1a1a;
      --mist: #444;
      --lotus: #444;
      --lantern: #444;
      --magnolia: #444;
      --tile-border: #ccc;
      --deep-sky: #ffffff;
    }
    :global(body) {
      background: white !important;
      color: black !important;
      font-size: 10pt;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    :global(body > header),
    :global(body > footer),
    :global(.skip-link) {
      display: none !important;
    }
    :global(main) {
      padding: 0 !important;
    }
    .cv {
      max-width: 100%;
    }
    .cv a {
      color: #1a1a1a;
      border-bottom: none;
    }
    .cv-head {
      padding-bottom: 0.75rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .cv-head h1 {
      font-size: 1.65rem;
    }
    .cv section {
      margin: 0.9rem 0;
    }
    .cv h2 {
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    .cv .projects, .cv .other {
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }
    .cv dl {
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }
  }

</style>